name: TRIBUTARY
description:
Come ye, come ye! Lift thy hand and enter. With river, rise, and with startide fill thy sky!

Our home runneth over; pouring forth as liquid electricity.

Melt, O MELT!

Quiet, the Earth - her children borne, and the ashes of olde; fuel to build the forest anew.

Process: Magick.
